{
  "stem": "22582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were 12 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we used to have-- we used to get-- we used to get coals coming in and sand coming in, and nothing attractive for us, at least, because we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But after-- and we were working under the Organisation Todt, which was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know how it worked, actually, with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were-- they were getting paid for every-- every person who was working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then in some cases, there was-- they were sending to work to factories and some places in constructions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were sending in the Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were to their disposition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a working organization, Nationale Socialistic, working organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had the brown uniforms, and-- with the swastika on the side on the arm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the guy in charge was a very-- a German, but wasn't Nazi, wasn't a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Work had to be done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And whoever was working good, with him, he was all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was satisfied with us, because when the train came in, we unloaded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we had a meister who was overseeing over us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were always satisfied, because as soon as a train came in, we unload in half an hour, an hour.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the beginning we had one, then two cars load, three car loads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Someday came seven car loads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we unloaded everything, because when we finished, we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They couldn't let us go, because they didn't know when the other train would come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes we can-- we could sit the whole day doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
